                    Welcome to Know Your Tank. When I first started out in the world of marine biology and fish keeping, there were so many terms,
                    factors and calculations that I just did not understand. It took hours of research to find the information I needed and why each
                    was important. The hardest thing I found was not having one resource that contained all the information you needed r was able to
                    direct you to where you need to go for further information. I have set up this website as a way to try and condense all the
                    information available into one place.
                    <br /><br />
                    Please note that the information provided in this website is for help and estimation purposes only. In this hobby things can
                    be more variable. Use this site and calculators for gudance purposes only.
                </p>
